BOSTON Northeastern Uni
versity has begun pilot program
to recruit promising Negro stu
dents who otherwise might not be
able to go to college.


Under $l5O,OOO grant from
the Fund for the Advancement
of Education, Northeastern will
enroll Is Negro students for each
of the next three years in its
cooperative plan of education.


The university has long &C
cepted Negro students. But the

new program, DR.. Asa Knowles
the president. said is designed to
meet a growing demand for Ne
groes in white collar jobs. Re-
cruitment will be in the metro
politan Boston area.


So far, five students out of
so applicants have been accepted
for enrolment next fall.


DR.. Knowles said many Ne
groes took vocational training in
high school on the theory they
could not hope for white collar
jobs.
